cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on developing an accurate Arabic lemmatizer algorithm for information retrieval (IR) systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with natural language processing (NLP) and computational linguistics. The paper also involves machine learning techniques and evaluation metrics, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves the use of different Arabic language knowledge resources, which is relevant to sub-category cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper's focus on information retrieval (IR) systems makes it relevant to sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
